PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 37 - which (a) DECLARES the forest fire in the community of Burwash Landing in the YUKON, which necessitated the evacuation of the community and caused damage to public and private property, to be of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.
